        <p>
            ZPHS PALAVALASA was established in 1962 and it is managed by the Local body. It is located in Rural area. It is located in GURLA block of VIZIANAGARAM district of ANDHRA PRADESH. The school consists of Grades from 6 to 10. The school is Co-educational and it doesn't have an attached pre-primary section. The school is Not Applicable in nature and is not using school building as a shift-school. Telugu is the medium of instructions in this school. This school is approachable by all weather road. In this school academic session starts in April.
         The school has N/A building. It has got 0 classrooms for instructional purposes. All the classrooms are in good condition. It has 2 other rooms for non-teaching activities. The school has a separate room for Head master/Teacher. The school has N/A boundary wall. The school has doesn't have electric connection. The source of Drinking Water in the school is None and it is functional. The school has 0 boys toilet and it is functional. and 0 girls toilet and it is functional. The school has no playground. The school has no library and has 0 books in its library. The school does not need ramp for disabled children to access classrooms.The school has no computers for teaching and learning purposes The school is not having a computer aided learning lab. The school is Not Applicable providing mid-day meal

<body>
    <h1>School Admission Form</h1>
    <div class="form-container">
        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="age">Age:</label>
                <input type="number" id="age" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="gender">Gender:</label>
                <select id="gender" required>
                    <option value="">Select Gender</option>
                    <option value="male">Male</option>
                    <option value="female">Female</option>
                    <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="moles">Moles:</label>
                <input type="text" id="moles" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="signature">Student Signature:</label>
                <input type="text" id="signature" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="address">Address:</label>
                <textarea id="address" rows="4" required></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="submit" value="Submit" onclick="showAlert()">
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showAlert() {
            alert("Your form is submitted");
        }
        
        
        
    </script><br><br>
